# Shine Codex Rules

- Load `.agents/skills/shine-project/SKILL.md` before repository work.
- Never edit `RobustToolbox/**`.
- Put new Shine code/resources under `_sh`.
- Mark non-`_sh` changes with `shine-edit start` / `shine-edit end`.
- Prefer prediction, localization, modular ECS, typed prototypes, and focused validation.
